high_descs: Go forward, around the counter in front of you and face the plate on the other side.
Pick up the plate from the counter.
Turn left, then left and face the microwave on top of the stove to your right.
Place the plate in the microwave and take it out.
Turn right and face the sink on your left.
Place the plate in the sink in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm plate in the sink.

high_descs: Walk across the kitchen, towards the windows, then make a left just before the window and go to the counter in front of the wooden stools, to your left.
Pick up the plate, on the counter, in front of the stools.
Turn around and make a right at the end of the counter, and go into the kitchen to the microwave above the stove on your right.
Place the plate in the microwave, heat it up, then remove the plate from the microwave.
Turn to your right and go to the sink on your left.
Place the plate in the open sink, on the right.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm plate in the sink.

high_descs: Walk forward to the counter and turn right, walk to counter with the black pot, turn right and walk four steps, turn right walking seven steps, turn left walking eight steps, turn right and stop in front of the counter.
Pick up the black plate on the counter.
Turn around and take one step, turn right and take eight steps, take a right and take 16 steps, turn right and walk toward the stove then stop and look up at the microwave.
Open the door to the microwave, put the plate in, turn on the microwave for a few seconds, open the door and remove the plate, close the microwave door.
Bring the plate down and turn right for five steps, turn left to face the sink.
Put the plate in the sink over the drain.
anns.task_desc: Place a black plate in the sink.
